            <div id="when-subcol-2" class="col-sm-6 col-md-6">
                <h3>What if I can't make the scheduled training or mission timees?</h3>

                <p>If you have the time, come and hang-out with us on TeamSpeak, there is usually always something
                    entertaining going on. If there's something in particular you would like to do, simply find someone
                    in the Commando Regiments with the rank of Lieutenant or above, or any of HQ J sections, or a member
                    of SOCOMD's Training Staff, and ask them to organise something, such as training or a mission.</p>
                <img src="img/When-do-u-play.jpg" style="padding-bottom: 5%">

                <p>It is important to note that all of our operations and training courses are scheduled through our
                    Steam Group Calendar to account for variations in time zones, so be sure to keep an eye on it to
                    know exactly when events are scheduled.</p>

